baby ignore karo ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
baby ignore karo  Example 05 — Conditionals
baby ignore karo  agar / warna / warna agar / bas itna hi
baby ignore karo ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

yaad score hai 87

~~ Natural style — preferred in Lovelang
agar score bada ya barabar hai 90 toh
  baby bolo na "A grade — bohot acha kiya 🏆"
warna agar score bada ya barabar hai 75 toh
  bolo "B grade — thoda aur mehnat karo"
warna agar score bada ya barabar hai 50 toh
  baby bolo naa "C grade — pass ho gaye, yeh bhi kuch kam nahi"
warna
  bolo "fail — ek baar aur try karo, tum kar sakte ho 💪"
bas itna hi

~~ Equality checks using word operators
yaad mood hai "shayari"

agar mood barabar hai "shayari" toh
  bolo "aaj lafzon mein baarish hai 🌧️"
warna agar mood barabar hai "toxic" toh
  bolo "tum woh nahi jo main chahta tha"
warna
  bolo "romantic mode on 🌹"
bas itna hi

~~ Inequality check
yaad reply hai null

agar reply barabar nahi null toh
  bolo "reply aaya!"
warna
  bolo "left on read... again 😔"
bas itna hi

~~ Boolean check
yaad online hai sach

agar online toh
  baby bolo naa "woh online hai — dil dhadak raha hai 💓"
warna
  bolo "offline hai... wait karo"
bas itna hi

~~ Compound conditions with aur / ya
yaad age hai 22
yaad has_job hai sach

agar age bada hai 18 aur has_job toh
  bolo "eligible ✅"
warna
  bolo "not yet..."
bas itna hi

love you baby byeee
